{"tid":1510313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涂謹申：料美國很大機會通過香港人權與民主法案","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:53:39.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da7802d0a7936c31e1def3920d74655b8621d4ec","tid":1510313,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">民主黨立法會議員涂謹申表示，美國國會很大機會將有至少三分之二議員，贊成通過《香港人權與民主法案》</span>，他估計法案的框架將會以《中英聯合聲明》作為基礎，訂立制裁香港官員的機制等，一旦法案獲得通過，美國總統特朗普無法否決。<br />\n<br />\n包括涂謹申和新民黨主席葉劉淑儀在內的6名立法會議員，早前獲邀到美國同數名國會議員討論香港近期局勢。<span style=\"color: red;\">涂謹申說，民主派和建制派議員在訪美過程中沒有共識，例如民主派由始至終都認為要成立獨立調查委員會。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，涂謹申認為，如果特區政府引用《緊急法》就等同宣布戒嚴，禁止市民集會示威，只會令「和理非」市民都同政府強烈對立，做法愚蠢，亦會影響香港的特殊貿易待遇，在現時中美貿易戰升級的形勢下，只會為國家添煩添亂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477073-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477073-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=1cfce7d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477073-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7a942581\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477073-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d4fbeb66fc034fb004b35438365680086fc04af3","tid":1510313,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=7040c9f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"